<h1>Guardian Upcoming Events</h1>

<section id="about">
	<a name="about"></a>
	<h2>About</h2>
	<div>
		This application is for managing the promotion of events on the Guardian through the Microapp framework. It has two purposes:
		<ul>
			<li>Promote an event and display a countdown clock, i.e. "2 days until the last day for Christmas post"</li>
			<li>Promote an event using descriptive text, i.e. "Visit us this Sunday for our Oscars coverage"</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
</section>